 seamless, AI-powered environment.</p><p>🌟 We’re proud to share that Flowie has been <strong>officially recognized by Gartner</strong> as a leading provider in the emerging category of <strong>Procurement Orchestration Platforms</strong> — a powerful validation of our vision and the incredible work of our team.</p><p>But our ambition goes beyond procurement. We are building a platform that could enable the world to truly <strong>understand what we are buying</strong> — by chaining supply data end-to-end. This means not only improving efficiency for enterprises, but also empowering society with <strong>transparency, sustainability, and accountability</strong> in global supply chains.</p><ul><li><strong>Global Ambition</strong> → Already operating in 3 countries, with 40 more on the roadmap.</li><li><strong>Proven Traction</strong> → From 0 to international enterprise clients in record time.</li><li><strong>AI at the Core</strong> → Automating, analyzing, and enabling smarter business decisions.</li><li><strong>Diverse &amp; Remote-Friendly</strong> → A team of 6+ nationalities, working across Europe, with a culture of ownership and excellence.</li><li><strong>Committed to Responsibility</strong> → ESG is part of our DNA: we are <strong>B Corp pending</strong>, engaged in <strong>Ecovadis certification</strong>, and committed to building a sustainable, ethical, and inclusive company.</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Our Stack</p><p>We run on a modern, event-driven architecture built for scale:</p><ul><li><strong>Backend</strong> → Scala, Node.js, Python macroservices</li><li><strong>Frontend</strong> → React, TypeScript (PWA)</li><li><strong>Events &amp; Data</strong> → Apache Pulsar, PostgreSQL, BigQuery, Neo4j</li><li><strong>Infrastructure</strong> → Kubernetes (GCP/Thales), Terraform</li><li><strong>Ops &amp; CI/CD</strong> → GitHub Actions, Sentry, Claude code, …</li><li><strong>AI &amp; GenAI</strong> → OpenAI, Anthropic, Mistral, Llama, Claude, orchestrated via MCP Serve